  "coherence": {
    "title": "Universal Coherence",
    "body": "This project exists because we share real minutes, seconds that align the pulse. Our flows of time touch one another and, in that contact, we understand that coherence is not declared: it is practiced. Thinking, feeling, and acting in the same direction, without \"ornaments\".\n\nMay this work serve as gratitude and as a commitment: to keep creating with ethics, joy, and respect for everything that connects us.\n\nWith affection,\nAndrés Calvo Espinosa\n\nPalma de Mallorca, November 7, 2025"
  }
